OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fbright spells after any lingering
OL,7,Fheavy showers clear. Then turning
OL,8,Fcloudier overnight with a risk of
OL,9,Ffurther showery rain in the early
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA bright but partly cloudy
OL,13,Fday with showers or longer spells of
OL,14,Frain, often heavy with a risk of
OL,15,Fthunder.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,18,FUnsettled and rather changeable
OL,19,Fthrough this period with showers or
OL,20,Flonger spells of rain. Often rather
OL,21,Fbreezy.
